                    a(href="#" class="block lg:inline-block mt-4 lg:mt-0 mr-10 text-blue-900 hover:text-blue-700" ) FAQ
                    a(href="#" class="block lg:inline-block mt-4 lg:mt-0 text-blue-900 hover:text-blue-700" ) Contact

            section(class="py-12 px-4 text-center")
                div(class="w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto")
                    span(class="text-sm font-semibold") Go from to-do to done
                    h2(class="text-5xl mt-2 mb-6 leading-tight font-heading") No project can be made without Collaboration
                    a(href="#" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline" ) Learn more &raquo;

            section(class="py-8 px-4")
                div(class="flex flex-wrap -mx-4 -mb-6")
                    div(class="lg:w-1/3 px-4 mb-6 hover:shadow-2xl")
                        img(src="placeholders/icons/shield.svg" alt="" )
                        h3(class="text-xl my-2 font-heading" ) High durability
                        p(class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed" ) Forget about paper jams with our increased stability product. Ideal for high-quality printing, colour printing and photocopying.
                    
                    div(class="lg:w-1/3 px-4 mb-6 hover:shadow-2xl")
                        img(src="placeholders/icons/cloud-tools.svg" alt="" )
                        h3(class="text-xl my-2 font-heading" ) Versatility
                        p(class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed" ) Multi-functional paper for various office needs. Snow-white sheets will shine bright like diamond for many years.
                    
                    div(class="lg:w-1/3 px-4 mb-6 hover:shadow-2xl")
                        img(src="placeholders/icons/cart.svg" alt="" )
                        h3(class="text-xl my-2 font-heading" ) Value-based price
                        p(class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed" ) The best combination of quality and economy comes with Dunder Mifflin paper. The offer includes paper in wide range of density and sizes.

            section(class="py-12 px-4")
                h2(class="text-3xl mb-8 text-center font-heading" ) How to get Dunder Mifflined?

                div(class="flex max-w-sm mb-10 mx-auto text-center border-b-2")
                    div(class="w-1/2 pb-2 border-b-4 border-indigo-500")
                        button For Customers
                    div(class="w-1/2 pb-2")
                        button For Companies

                div(class="flex flex-wrap -mx-8")
                    div(class="lg:w-1/3 px-8 mb-8 lg:mb-0")
                        img(src="placeholders/icons/mobile.svg" alt="" )
                        h3(class="text-2xl mb-3 font-heading" ) Contact our Sales
                        p(class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed" ) During the phone call we will be able to present you all details of cooperation, pricing and special offers, suited for your company.
                    
                    div(class="lg:w-1/3 px-8 mb-8 lg:mb-0")
                        img(src="placeholders/icons/pen.svg" alt="" )
                        h3(class="text-2xl mb-3 font-heading" ) Sign the documents
                        p(class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed" ) We can also talk during business meeting, or visit your office anytime you want! Our employees will provide proper contracts.
                    
                    div(class="lg:w-1/3 px-8 mb-8 lg:mb-0")
                        img(src="placeholders/icons/van.svg" alt="" )
                        h3(class="text-2xl mb-3 font-heading" ) Wait for delivery!
                        p(class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed" ) You don’t buy a pig... or shall I say a paper in a poke. The supplies will be delivered to your company every first Monday of the month.

            section(class="py-12 px-4 text-center")
                h2(class="text-4xl mb-2 leading-tight font-heading") Collaboration Family
                p(class="max-w-xl mx-auto mb-12 text-gray-500") Because no product could exist without teamwork, skills, perseverance and of course-collaboration!

                div(class="flex flex-wrap -mx-8")
                    div(class="md:w-1/3 p-8")
                        img(src="placeholders/pictures/female_avatar.svg" alt="" class="w-1/3 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full" )
                        h3(class="text-xl font-heading") Nikita Jain
                        span Regional Manager
                        p(class="mt-4 text-gray-500 leading-relaxed" ) Started as a Sales representative at Stamford branch, moved to Scranton. All of us left as soon as possible except for Andy.
                    
                    div(class="md:w-1/3 p-8 md:border-l")
                        img(src="placeholders/pictures/male_avatar.svg" alt="" class="w-1/3 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full" ) 
                        h3(class="text-xl font-heading") Shreya Prasad
                        span Marketing Director
                        p(class="mt-4 text-gray-500 leading-relaxed" ) The warehouse is not a piece of cake, man. I started there as an Assistant and finally got a promotion to the Marketing Director.
                    
                    div(class="md:w-1/3 p-8 md:border-l")
                        img(src="placeholders/pictures/female_avatar.svg" alt="" class="w-1/3 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full" )

                        h3(class="text-xl font-heading") Lakshmi Pandey
                        span Customer Service
                        p(class="mt-4 text-gray-500 leading-relaxed" ) I work for Dunder Mifflin for a few years now. I learned a lot. You know, one person department is not easy to manage.

            section(class="py-12 px-4")
                div(class="max-w-3xl mx-auto")
                    h2(class="text-4xl text-center mb-4 font-heading" ) Frequently Asked Questions

                    div(class="p-4 mb-2 border-b")
                        button(class="flex w-full text-left")
                            span(class="flex-grow font-semibold") How does Collaborations differ from other products?
                            img(src="placeholders/icons/angle-bottom.svg" alt="" class="w-12" )
                        p(class="mt-1" ) Paper produced with love, devotion, passion - is not the same paper. Our supplies are extra strong, and you’re going to need the paper-tear up-master to destroy just one sheet. It’s also suited for every available printer.

                    div(class="p-4 mb-2 border-b")
                        button(class="flex w-full text-left")
                            span(class="flex-grow font-semibold" ) Why choose Dunder Mifflin instead of some huge paper producer?
                            img(src="placeholders/icons/angle-bottom.svg" alt="" class="w-12" )
                        p(class="hidden mt-1" ) You know that feeling when you are waiting on the phone for hours to contact your supplier? Sometimes they even have a waiting time music prepared for that. In Dunder Mifflin, you can get help immediately, and each of our customers receives an individual assistant. For us, companies are people - not numbers, so we take care of each of them.

                    div(class="p-4 mb-2 border-b")
                        button(class="flex w-full text-left")
                            span(class="flex-grow font-semibold" ) When I will receive the products?
                            img(src="placeholders/icons/angle-bottom.svg" alt="" class="w-12" )
                        p(class="hidden mt-1" ) If you buy one of our business plans, you will receive the supplies every first Monday of the month. However, you can also purchase paper separately. Our employees will make sure that you will receive the products in the next business days.

                    div(class="p-4 mb-2 border-b")
                        button(class="flex w-full text-left")
                            span(class="flex-grow font-semibold" ) How long does it take to finalize the deal?
                            img(src="placeholders/icons/angle-bottom.svg" alt="" class="w-12" )
                        p(class="hidden mt-1" ) The whole process depends on your decision. If you sign the contract immediately, we can start official cooperation in the next two business days.

            section(class="py-12 px-4")
                h2(class="text-3xl mb-8 text-center font-heading" ) Contact the Scranton team

                div(class="w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8")
                    form
                        div(class="flex mb-4 -mx-2")
                            div(class="w-1/2 px-2")
                                input(class="appearance-none block w-full py-3 px-4 leading-tight text-gray-700 bg-gray-200 focus:bg-white border border-gray-200 focus:border-gray-500 rounded focus:outline-none" type="email" placeholder="Name")
                            div(class="w-1/2 px-2")
                                input(class="appearance-none block w-full py-3 px-4 leading-tight text-gray-700 bg-gray-200 focus:bg-white border border-gray-200 focus:border-gray-500 rounded focus:outline-none" type="email" placeholder="Email")
                        div(class="mb-4")
                            textarea(class="appearance-none block w-full py-3 px-4 leading-tight text-gray-700 bg-gray-200 focus:bg-white border border-gray-200 focus:border-gray-500 rounded focus:outline-none" type="password" placeholder="Write something..." rows="5")
                        div
                            button(class="inline-block w-full py-4 px-8 leading-none text-white bg-indigo-500 hover:bg-indigo-600 rounded shadow" ) Submit

                div(class="text-center")
                    p(class="mb-2" ) Or just email us on
                    a(href="#" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline" ) scranton@dundermifflin.com

